si_remarks: The younger of two sites close to Skyttorp that have been part of a chronosequency study together with Norunda in CarboAge. The site is Sky2 in the fluxnet  network. Sapflow data are unpublished. Some description in CA reports found here: http://www.eeo.ed.ac.uk/abs/research/carboage/reports.html
